ss="_ _6"></span>尤其是<span class="_ _9"></span>《百业经》<span class="_ _7"></span>、<span class="_ _c"></span>《长阿含经》<span class="_ _7"></span>、<span class="_ _c"></span>《杂阿含</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y186 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls36 ws0">经》<span class="_ _7"></span><span class="ls0">、<span class="_ _7"></span><span class="ls43">《毗奈耶经》<span class="_ _7"></span><span class="ls50">，就会明白凡事都有前因后果，也会懂<span class="_ _1"></span>得</span></span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y17f ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls20 ws0">在漫长的轮回中，<span class="_ _6"></span>众生之间是如何冤冤相报的。<span class="_ _6"></span>所以，<span class="_ _6"></span>大家</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y26 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">最好是看一些佛教公案，这样才会了知其中的甚深意义。 </div><div class="t m0 x67 h23 y199 ff15 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls4d ws0">（八） <span class="_ _e"> </span><span class="ff16 ls0">问<span class="ff4 fs3 ls4e">：我是浙江工业大学播音系的大学生。前</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h17 y172 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">段时间，<span class="_ _8"></span>有件事情对我影响特别大：<span class="_ _8"></span>我的一个好朋友得了红</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
